  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "d1e65f55f37cd02f3d1612821f9876415cb14a3584eac9c8825a80df7bb67da1": "Welcome to the 10th squad, [?].",
    "c5457c830632e4deb9f1c88ff925d8dd80d0e6a4ee91d39e1bfd1f917fa237e9": "Welcome back, [?].",
    "85fe3dc4a5b75aa01483ed310503b0c9639b35dd6e460cf20932719611048446": "Good luck, [?].",
    "162f830cc8c1cc00f4e5d28928edca9ec0117781164e4798f3e8e97c7976dc0a": "We can't give up, [?], come back when you've got more information.",
    "974b8e7868e4fe8583417a5bab9dd67079a53599299ad9a2099e893400d743d0": "Please hurry [?], we need this information from Awowogei before it's too late.",
    "c80cae0dd082e19f16bfe8eec2f57f839c7d3a45b4e447f0c23837b222c5fc0e": "Excellent work, [?].",
    "266b7bf49852425f53cc6c1842a9481869c3a09565e5e175ccb16634beaeb6c9": "Excellent, [?]!",
    "5a977dfa41ddbd6c22bf390291cdf0c1d15dfb2a479c549bef156ef730714b94": "I'm sure you'll find a way, [?].",
    "0752f45841d48fa8924c85f910e1e9ce0a654573011c7bf0a876fec299171f51": "Please hurry, [?], we need to find out what we're up against here.",
    "78cc257f850b6787c23bf64960ad699a5ebaa045d9df154be16350fc7df12006": "Good work, [?]! Now all that's left to do is inform Awowogei of his failed plans. If he has any sense, he will call off his plans for attack.",
    "a573eeb9ff6e6ca2dc48e2c6b18ff2fb608b029f90694938a33c2df42e703c51": "Please hurry, [?], we are so close to victory!",
    "670008bb3f9eec64b80a67e7660026d80507703ef4774dcf75c7c4561420db51": "I knew you could do it, [?]!",
    "8cd9df802b75549bf3c6eb117190a1ab1c12a89fed1350bb4856a3d2d0dac9c0": "You said you dealt with the airships, [?]!",
    "245441af93b1d2bf5f647c36daa0c86fe08174defac32243eb090fbcb1835583": "There's no time for chatting, [?]! You need to get back to the Gnome Stronghold!",
    "b1c3621cb14166a1b7eb960990cc367bde5ecce0bd7d83c6369ebad232bdc772": "Some of those things have made it into the Stronghold, you've got to defeat them, [?]!",
    "6f0dd627e5363b502a626bd2866269cc931d426a6079d55786645e6fcd8da8fc": "We'll keep the breach secure, [?]. You should head to the crash site to make sure Glough is dealt with, once and for all.",
    "68ab21442a8980cbd34215cb266cc288c6185a3b48e6f81a4e442af559404cbb": "I know you're tough, [?], but it would be unwise to head out there on your own. Get Nieve and then come back.",
    "4c70b3322757007f4f2d420364c0aff3cabbe7a61e0193b2f41d2505a68cdcca": "Greetings, [?].",
    "d9b7bc8979b975c792275550bcd3a5b6b35ee456c7fece1fc0bf14f08739e629": "Always good to see you again, [?]."
  }
}